        </p>

    </div>

    <div class="gallery-grid">

        <div class="gallery-card gallery-large">
            <img src="img/gallery/gallery1-new.jpg?v=3" alt="Gunung Kinabalu">
            <div class="gallery-overlay">
                <h3>Gunung Kinabalu</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery-card">
            <img src="img/gallery/gallery2.jpg" alt="Desa Dairy Farm">
            <div class="gallery-overlay">
                <h3>Desa Dairy Farm</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery-card">
            <img src="img/gallery/gallery3.jpg" alt="Kundasang Market">
            <div class="gallery-overlay">
                <h3>Kundasang Market</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery-card gallery-wide">
            <img src="img/gallery/gallery4.jpg" alt="Sosodikon Hill">
